Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦测到敌人一架郁金香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入第二防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:42.71,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,0)\bord0\shad0\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(302,380)\fscy150\fs58\1a&H43&}『女人味』是危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查回收坠落在迪尼西安岛可能是新型的郁金香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与我的抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有如此优秀的我们才会被指派的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人听我的命令到舰桥来  这是怎么回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我说明吧  现在当地时间是上午十点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是日本所谓的丑时三刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候当然该在房间睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么话？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子是军舰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你不是操舵士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以离开岗位?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经换班了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣凑  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长到底跑到那去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于赤道上的迪尼西安岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚礁  还有沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是太懒散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有必要先把那些东西准备好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当年我年轻的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我不能只是等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须向小惠看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样为他准备宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你突然借厨房打算做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香  太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何料理都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的就只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河也真多灾多难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空虚啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么才能填满我这空虚的心灵呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就..就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了爱的宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我而做的宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿纯  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百..百合香?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我什么也想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正演到精彩的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先让我看看你的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  我为你做了宵夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在看动画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次穿这种衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不适合？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不  非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第三十三集的"圣少女艾卡玛琳的微笑"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是主角的敌人双子座机器人的少女艾卡玛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为意外而失去记忆和男主角恋爱的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个客串的艾卡玛琳是个很好的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很会作菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢会作菜的女孩啊  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  这是百合香特地为你作的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧  不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝这个营养果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这像毒气般的臭味是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不  那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠  你到底放了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琵草  山椒  香菇  牛羞  莲藕  鳖与蝮蛇的鲜血  牛肝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再与市面上卖的营养药剂混合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是吃了什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上送他去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个锅拿去焚化!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是木星蜥蜴的新的攻击方式吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是恋爱的猛药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要结婚的话一定娶个会烧一手好菜的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  这次我为你做了好吃的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  激钢人3!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明..明人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么  艾卡玛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡玛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健  虽然非常短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能跟你在一起我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡玛琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡玛琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这种女孩的话就不必伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面的岩礁处降落到水面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家准备登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃琉璃  你的皮肤白用这个防晒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次到海边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳伞部队  赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别输给女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可是受雇于NERGAL重工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游玩的时间要扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是我写的海滩备忘录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在岩石上要穿拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防晒油除了具自然分解性的以外都禁止使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的! 把影印本好好看一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水浴场的三大名产就是这粉粉的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃的拉面还有溶化的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已把这传统延续至今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一子相传最后的海滩茶屋师傅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁倒了  不倒翁倒了  不倒翁倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从火星来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  天河君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  我的白后王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡玛琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你们这些人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是怎么一回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知不知道现在可不是玩的时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探查新型郁金香要怎么办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要太过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  埋起来埋起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟敢这样对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是提督  提督…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们快放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..我叫天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人跑到哪里去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我艾卡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡  你一个人住在这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲母亲都过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是举目无亲  孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  该开始探查了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会在那里溺水了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来明人还有惠也不见了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这..这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一队人就不必替他们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛好象是最近才变成私有土地的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是澳洲最大联合企业的老板克里逊家的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里逊家?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在最近  克里逊的独生女在社交界出道成为话题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里逊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在防壁方面是世上顶尖的武器制造商
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个防壁卫星也是向他们订购的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这财阀的独生女好象是个问题女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题女？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是在宴会上所有客人的料理中放麻痹药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了画自己的少女漫画去绑架漫画家未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对克里逊家来说她是唯一的污点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是新型的郁金香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么摧毁它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里逊家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁? 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多想  破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么克里逊家的防壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从爸爸妈妈过世之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直是一个人生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我遇见了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言你是我终于找到的白马王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我来说也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要永远跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大的蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型郁金香看来不是玻色子跳跃的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是那个巨大家伙的搬运密封舱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们也在尝试各种战法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还不是完全的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它给解决掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  这女孩是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你快点离开明人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦  她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的艾卡玛琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于要迎接最后的时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战火中消失  相爱的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾..艾..艾卡  你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的死去  相爱的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  那时候我就是悲剧的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  你赶快离开那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快点放开明人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子放在食物里的麻醉剂开始生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要做这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死的话自己一个人死就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会了解?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自小以来我就过得无拘无束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西垂手可得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直向往着悲剧的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于幸福就是我的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和心爱的男人双双死于战火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个郁金香是神赐给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  我不会离开你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人要在这里美丽地消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐  你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉子  后面后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  干掉它干掉它
