Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃过那女孩的料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的料理就不能吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 我不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我试着为你做了料理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
